        {
            "title": "半日收市︱轉呈橫行 恒指跌45點報24727點 阿里、美團轉身撐市 英諾賽科飆逾30%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股在8月開局首半日呈窄幅橫行，升與跌均在百點以內。憧憬內地外賣平台競爭轉緩，美團(03690)與阿里巴巴(09988)頓成撐市主力。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團2024年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_03690-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團2024年度年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_03690-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團2024年度年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開28點後進入好淡爭持，初段最高只見24856點，升83點，低位24693點時亦只跌80點；恒指中午收報24727點，跌45點或0.18%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團2024年度年報\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_03690-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團2024年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_03690-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：美團2024年度年報</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"美團 餓了麼\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250801-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"美團 餓了麼\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250801-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">美團 餓了麼</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"中通快遞\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02057.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"中通快遞\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02057.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">中通快遞</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：英偉達官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_FI_source-web_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：英偉達官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_FI_source-web_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：英偉達官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團2024年度年報\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_03690-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：美團2024年度年報</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"美團 餓了麼\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250801-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">美團 餓了麼</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"中通快遞\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02057.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">中通快遞</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：英偉達官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_FI_source-web_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：英偉達官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數也跌6點或0.12%，報5446點；國企指數跌不足1點或0.01%，報8882點。主板半日成交1197.97億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌47點，報24699點，低水29點。科指期貨跌2點，報5451點，高水4點。國指期貨跌6點，報8879點，低水3點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">投資者今早焦點放在內地不同行業「內捲式」競爭有望緩和的憧憬上，最明顯的是內地外賣平台以補貼進行價格競爭，隨著兩大業內巨擘美團以及阿里巴巴旗下淘寶閃購與餓了麼，相繼發文籲抵制無序競爭，令人揣測業內惡性競爭情況有望改善。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美團 餓了麼\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250801-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美團 餓了麼\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250801-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美團 餓了麼</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在上述消息於上午大約11時前後被傳泛報道後，美團股價隨即抽升，最高曾見125.9元，反彈3.54%；中午收報124.3元，仍漲2.7元或2.22%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">有AI概念支持的阿里巴巴，今早股價全程報升，最高報119.3元，漲3.11%；中午收報118.4元，升2.7元或2.33%。單是美團與阿里巴巴，已為恒指提升68點進賬。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一邊廂，上月國家郵政局召開快遞企業座談會，就依法依規治理行業「內捲式」競爭，強化農村地區領取快件違規收費等突出問題整治，促進行業高質量發展進行座談交流。投資者隨即憧憬內地快遞行業惡性競爭情況將有變，快遞股今早應聲炒上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中通快遞\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02057.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中通快遞\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/02057.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中通快遞</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中通快遞(02057)曾飆11.13%，高見168.8元；中午收報165元，仍漲13.1元或8.62%，毫無懸念登上藍籌升幅榜首，成交增至11.37億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他快遞股亦造好，極兔速遞(01519)漲4.65%，報10.8元；順豐控股(06936)升2.06%，報44.6元。京東物流(02618)也升2.05%，報13.94元；同系京東(09618)升1.38%，報124.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金融股與油股則拖低大市，友邦保險(01299)跌1.23%，報72.5元；滙控(00005)績後持續受壓，今早再跌0.57%，報95.6元；港交所(00388)也跌1.31%，報421.4元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際油價回吐，「三桶油」全線報跌。中國石化(00386)發盈警，沽壓自然較大，跌4.78%，報4.38元；中國石油(00857)跌2.22%，報7.5元；中海油(00883)跌0.43%，報18.8元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：英偉達官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_FI_source-web_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：英偉達官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250715_FI_source-web_Nvidia-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：英偉達官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，英偉達官網今早更新800V直流電源架構合作商名錄，英諾賽科(02577)成為今次入選合作伙伴中唯一的中國芯片企業。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英諾賽科股價在早市收市前約10分鐘急彈，兩次觸發市調機制，股價急飆30.68%，報57.5元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15139644-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e8%bd%89%e5%91%88%e6%a9%ab%e8%a1%8c-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c45%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124727%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e3%80%81%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%98%e8%bd%89",
