        {
            "title": "美團、淘寶閃購及餓了麼相繼發文籲抵制無序競爭",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地媒體報道，美團(03690)以及阿里巴巴(09988)旗下淘寶閃購與餓了麼，相繼發文呼籲抵制無序競爭。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250703-190807_20250617_CR_外賣_外賣員_速遞員_單車_美團_source-bp_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/bplib_20250703-190807_20250617_CR_外賣_外賣員_速遞員_單車_美團_source-bp_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">淘寶閃購及餓了麼發文名為《持續提升服務推動良性競爭激發消費煙火》，美團發文則以《繁榮產業生態，抵制無序競爭》為題，先後提及不以顯著低於成本的價格銷售商品和服務，嚴重扭曲價格信號，擾亂市場競爭秩序，造成浪費，堅決抵制惡性競爭。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">近期內地外賣平台掀起一片內捲式補貼競價，事件引發廣泛關注，據報市監局等機構早前已先後約談美團、餓了麼及京東(09618)等平台，要求公平有序競爭。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15139343-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%98%e3%80%81%e6%b7%98%e5%af%b6%e9%96%83%e8%b3%bc%e5%8f%8a%e9%a4%93%e4%ba%86%e9%ba%bc%e7%9b%b8%e7%b9%bc%e7%99%bc%e6%96%87%e7%b1%b2%e6%8a%b5%e5%88%b6%e7%84%a1%e5%ba%8f%e7%ab%b6%e7%88%ad",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250801-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-01 11:15:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "發改委：第4批消費品以舊換新資金將於10月下達 涉690億元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">發展委體改司副司長蔣毅今早在新聞發布會上表示，今年第3批690億元(人民幣‧下同)支持消費品以舊換新的超長期特別國債資金已全部下達完畢。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-ap_China.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-ap_China.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他進一步表示，將於10月按計劃下達第4批690億元消費品以舊換新資金，屆時將完成今年3000億元的資金下達計劃。</p>\n</div>",
